title: 100 Weeknight Curries by Madhur Jaffrey
description:
Simple curries, perfect for cooking up quickly during the week, from the world authority on Indian food. There are plenty of family-favorite recipes here, including creamy kormas and stir-fried prawns as well as satisfying stews, quick kebabs, and light suppers and snacks.
